---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="홈">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>AI의 문턱을 낮추다</h1>
    <p class="tagline">모든 사람이 AI를 누릴 수 있도록 하는 Sudoremove</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/community/docs" class="btn btn-primary">문서 보기</a>
      <a href="/community/board" class="btn btn-secondary">커뮤니티 참여</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <h2>우리가 하는 일</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>AI 교육</h3>
        <p>Physical AI부터 LLM까지, 실무 중심의 AI 교육을 제공합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>커뮤니티</h3>
        <p>함께 배우고 성장하는 AI 학습 커뮤니티를 운영합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>오픈소스</h3>
        <p>모든 교육 자료와 코드를 공개하여 누구나 학습할 수 있습니다.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="current-focus">
    <h2>현재 진행 중</h2>
    <div class="focus-content">
      <h3>HuggingFace LeRobot을 활용한 Physical AI</h3>
      <p>로봇공학과 AI를 결합한 실습 중심 교육 프로그램을 준비하고 있습니다.</p>
      <a href="/community/docs/physical-ai/getting-started" class="btn btn-primary">자세히 보기</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #e94560, #f5f5f5);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent-color);
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #d63850;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    color: white;
    border: 2px solid var(--accent-color);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--accent-color);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .features {
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .features h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: var(--secondary-color);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .current-focus {
    background: var(--primary-color);
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .current-focus h2 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .focus-content h3 {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .focus-content p {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
